STl- Standard Template Library 
It basically is a library having various templates like vectors<> & stack & etc.
  It consists of 3 major parts
(i)Container- It is used to store data .(Vector,Stack)
(ii)Iterator-It is used to traverse because it act as a pointer as we can call a bookmark.
(iii)Algorithm-It is in-built funtion that is used to perform actions on the data.
